WEBVTT

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:40.580
=Reincarnated Love=

00:00:40.780 --> 00:00:43.700
=Episode 18=

00:00:53.060 --> 00:00:55.100
(10th lifetime)

00:01:04.860 --> 00:01:05.700
(Stabbed to death)

00:01:05.700 --> 00:01:06.700
(Stabbed and pushed)

00:01:08.380 --> 00:01:09.420
(Fell to death)

00:01:09.420 --> 00:01:10.540
(Pushed off the rockery)

00:01:13.300 --> 00:01:14.920
(3rd lifetime, Suffocated)

00:01:14.931 --> 00:01:17.224
(Abducted and suffocated
while bidding farewell to Ruoli)

00:01:21.530 --> 00:01:22.880
♪Where shall I seek♪

00:01:22.900 --> 00:01:23.649
(Stabbed to death)

00:01:23.660 --> 00:01:24.580
(Stabbed in the crowd)

00:01:24.580 --> 00:01:25.326
(Poisoned to death)

00:01:25.337 --> 00:01:26.340
(Trying Ruoli's favorite)

00:01:26.340 --> 00:01:27.620
(6th lifetime, Shot with arrows)

00:01:27.620 --> 00:01:28.940
(Ambushed and killed by arrows)

00:01:31.580 --> 00:01:34.340
(9th lifetime,
Stabbed to death by Ruoli)

00:01:37.540 --> 00:01:41.380
(9th lifetime,
Stabbed to death by Ruoli)

00:01:44.080 --> 00:01:48.770
♪Dreams lift the night
where stars grow thin♪

00:01:52.340 --> 00:01:54.020
(9th lifetime,
Stabbed to death by Ruoli)

00:01:54.020 --> 00:02:00.220
The 10th lifetime.

00:02:00.220 --> 00:02:05.560
♪If I could, let me guard you this time♪

00:02:05.980 --> 00:02:10.540
(I want to grow old with you)

00:02:11.190 --> 00:02:12.400
For all the remaining years,

00:02:13.310 --> 00:02:15.190
I'll do everything to keep you safe

00:02:16.033 --> 00:02:16.920
and never abandon you.

00:02:16.920 --> 00:02:19.360
♪A fleeting dream
shines through the rain♪

00:02:19.610 --> 00:02:21.790
♪Through three lifetimes,
we never part♪

00:02:22.400 --> 00:02:26.170
♪A thousand years of snow
fall into your palm♪

00:02:26.190 --> 00:02:27.030
I once promised

00:02:28.310 --> 00:02:30.400
to keep you safe for a lifetime.

00:02:30.810 --> 00:02:33.310
♪Each thought recalls the past♪

00:02:33.520 --> 00:02:36.140
♪Longing burns into a lasting ache♪

00:02:36.350 --> 00:02:38.720
♪Frost stains the white robes♪

00:02:39.150 --> 00:02:41.720
♪Mist and clouds veil the sky♪

00:02:41.930 --> 00:02:44.130
♪My past was filled with you alone♪

00:02:44.140 --> 00:02:49.300
(I want to grow old with you)

00:02:49.360 --> 00:02:53.180
♪Our love♪

00:02:55.360 --> 00:02:56.310
From this moment on,

00:02:57.360 --> 00:02:58.470
you and I should go

00:02:59.190 --> 00:03:00.310
our separate ways.

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:02.080
I'm sorry.

00:03:02.740 --> 00:03:05.300
(I want to grow old with you)

00:03:05.310 --> 00:03:06.240
I'm sorry.

00:03:08.710 --> 00:03:10.710
The nuptial wine
is meant for a real couple.

00:03:11.910 --> 00:03:15.590
You and I are merely allies
with mutual interests.

00:03:18.340 --> 00:03:21.500
♪I'd spend a lifetime's luck
just for you♪

00:03:21.520 --> 00:03:22.360
It's all my fault.

00:03:23.910 --> 00:03:28.920
♪Gazing at your figure
for the rest of my life♪

00:03:29.150 --> 00:03:33.370
♪Until time grows us old♪

00:03:33.400 --> 00:03:35.960
(In every life, Yanzhi was killed
by Lu Huaijin,)

00:03:36.910 --> 00:03:39.590
(except for the ninth,
where I killed him.)

00:03:40.310 --> 00:03:42.960
(Perhaps, this is the solution.)

00:03:43.520 --> 00:03:45.446
(I want to grow old with you)
Whatever the cost,

00:03:45.910 --> 00:03:47.910
I must change how our story ends.

00:03:47.990 --> 00:03:50.790
♪Fate never flows away♪

00:03:51.130 --> 00:03:56.620
♪If I could, let me guard you this time♪

00:03:56.620 --> 00:03:59.300
♪How did this feeling begin♪

00:03:59.550 --> 00:04:01.940
♪In each trial, longing deepens♪

00:04:02.210 --> 00:04:04.850
♪Across vast lands, it still shines♪

00:04:04.990 --> 00:04:07.560
♪When the night fades,
the moon shines longer♪

00:04:07.880 --> 00:04:10.420
♪A fleeting dream
shines through the rain♪

00:04:10.670 --> 00:04:12.850
♪Through three lifetimes,
we never part♪

00:04:12.850 --> 00:04:14.620
(9th lifetime,
Stabbed to death by Ruoli)

00:04:15.160 --> 00:04:18.870
♪Fall into your palm♪

00:04:19.000 --> 00:04:21.460
♪How did this feeling begin♪

00:04:21.870 --> 00:04:24.370
♪In each trial, longing deepens♪

00:04:24.580 --> 00:04:27.200
♪Across vast lands, it still shines♪

00:04:27.410 --> 00:04:29.780
♪When the night fades,
the moon shines longer♪

00:04:30.210 --> 00:04:32.780
♪A fleeting dream
shines through the rain♪

00:04:32.990 --> 00:04:35.560
♪Through three lifetimes,
we never part♪

00:04:35.770 --> 00:04:41.190
♪A thousand years of snow
fall into your palm♪

00:04:41.420 --> 00:04:43.880
♪How does love fade away♪

00:04:44.210 --> 00:04:46.790
♪Each thought recalls the past♪

00:04:46.900 --> 00:04:49.230
♪Longing burns into a lasting ache♪

00:04:49.610 --> 00:04:52.200
♪Frost stains the white robes♪

00:04:52.520 --> 00:04:55.170
♪Mist and clouds veil the sky♪

00:04:55.320 --> 00:04:57.850
♪My past was filled with you alone♪

00:04:58.070 --> 00:05:02.420
♪All our joy and sorrow shaped♪

00:05:02.730 --> 00:05:06.660
♪Our love♪

00:05:14.340 --> 00:05:18.060
(Huo Mansion)

00:05:32.950 --> 00:05:33.790
(What's this?)

00:05:35.680 --> 00:05:37.310
(Huo Linchuan has died ten times.)

00:05:38.390 --> 00:05:41.270
(Why hasn't the cycle I started ended?)

00:05:47.120 --> 00:05:48.240
Mr. Lu,

00:05:48.251 --> 00:05:50.044
the Jiang carriage
has reached the city gate.

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:53.120
(The Jiang carriage?)

00:05:54.360 --> 00:05:56.310
(Is Yuan returning
to the capital today?)

00:05:59.480 --> 00:06:00.320
Mr. Lu,

00:06:00.447 --> 00:06:02.293
Miss Jiang returns
from the countryside today.

00:06:02.360 --> 00:06:03.310
As you instructed,

00:06:03.830 --> 00:06:05.796
Luoxiang Pastry,
Miss Jiang's favorite, is ready.

00:06:24.120 --> 00:06:25.000
Jiang Ruoli,

00:06:26.600 --> 00:06:28.480
since reincarnation is not over,

00:06:29.430 --> 00:06:30.360
this time,

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:32.600
your affection

00:06:34.070 --> 00:06:35.390
will belong to me alone.

00:06:40.460 --> 00:06:43.580
(Jiang Mansion)

00:06:50.600 --> 00:06:51.630
Careful.

00:06:59.700 --> 00:07:01.940
(Jiang Mansion)

00:07:18.680 --> 00:07:19.520
Yuan.

00:07:26.480 --> 00:07:27.446
(That look in her eyes.)

00:07:28.750 --> 00:07:29.950
(Does she remember?)

00:07:32.310 --> 00:07:33.310
Yunzhou,

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:35.360
it's really you.

00:07:35.830 --> 00:07:37.263
I knew your journey would be tiring,

00:07:37.510 --> 00:07:40.190
so I got you
your favorite Luoxiang Pastry.

00:07:44.920 --> 00:07:46.000
Yunzhou,

00:07:46.390 --> 00:07:47.456
you actually remembered it.

00:07:48.053 --> 00:07:49.626
We've known each other
since childhood.

00:07:49.750 --> 00:07:51.510
Though we haven't met these past years,

00:07:52.510 --> 00:07:54.240
we've always written letters.

00:07:54.360 --> 00:07:55.326
Why would we be distant?

00:07:57.120 --> 00:07:57.960
Oh, right.

00:07:58.510 --> 00:08:00.010
I heard the Lantern Festival this year

00:08:00.480 --> 00:08:01.390
is going to be grand.

00:08:01.720 --> 00:08:02.780
There won't be any curfews.

00:08:02.920 --> 00:08:04.000
If you're free,

00:08:04.800 --> 00:08:06.070
would you like to go with me?

00:08:07.120 --> 00:08:07.980
I'd love to.

00:08:08.070 --> 00:08:08.910
It's settled then.

00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:10.720
I'll take my leave.

00:08:16.870 --> 00:08:17.710
Alright.

00:08:21.020 --> 00:08:22.530
There's a lion dance ahead.

00:08:29.380 --> 00:08:31.430
Great!

00:08:39.280 --> 00:08:40.320
This is impressive.

00:08:43.480 --> 00:08:45.480
The Lantern Festival
is truly lively this year.

00:08:45.480 --> 00:08:47.240
Ruoli, this is the capital after all.

00:08:47.240 --> 00:08:48.153
Of course, it's lively.

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:50.200
One more!

00:08:55.120 --> 00:08:55.960
Yunzhou.

00:08:57.600 --> 00:08:58.480
Nice to meet you.

00:08:59.150 --> 00:08:59.990
Mm.

00:09:00.960 --> 00:09:01.840
Yunzhou,

00:09:01.840 --> 00:09:02.680
this is my uncle.

00:09:03.720 --> 00:09:05.000
And this is his daughter.

00:09:05.000 --> 00:09:05.840
Mr. Lu.

00:09:07.200 --> 00:09:08.360
Father, Mother.

00:09:08.630 --> 00:09:10.200
The lanterns over there are beautiful.

00:09:10.390 --> 00:09:11.456
I'd like to go take a look.

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:13.080
Go ahead.

00:09:13.600 --> 00:09:17.000
Young folks should find
some joy of their own.

00:09:17.320 --> 00:09:18.160
Alright.

00:09:18.910 --> 00:09:20.183
(I never expected in this life)

00:09:20.720 --> 00:09:22.550
(Ruoli would treat me so warmly.)

00:09:22.720 --> 00:09:23.720
You're not allowed to go.

00:09:24.600 --> 00:09:25.440
Father.

00:09:25.750 --> 00:09:26.790
If you talk back,

00:09:27.030 --> 00:09:28.456
you'll be confined for half a month.

00:09:30.580 --> 00:09:31.440
Yunzhou.

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:32.280
Let's go.

00:09:36.550 --> 00:09:37.600
Yunzhou?

00:09:39.670 --> 00:09:40.510
Let's go.

00:09:49.620 --> 00:09:52.900
(Hongyun Troupe)

00:09:58.960 --> 00:10:00.240
I haven't returned for years.

00:10:00.480 --> 00:10:03.270
I didn't expect
such a grand festival here.

00:10:04.120 --> 00:10:04.960
Yuan,

00:10:06.080 --> 00:10:06.920
look.

00:10:07.790 --> 00:10:09.436
It's what you pestered me for
as a child.

00:10:12.150 --> 00:10:13.670
You remember everything so clearly,

00:10:14.120 --> 00:10:16.320
including the little things I like.

00:10:16.670 --> 00:10:17.510
Of course.

00:10:17.510 --> 00:10:19.120
I remember everything about you.

00:10:22.480 --> 00:10:23.750
There's a riddle arena up ahead.

00:10:24.200 --> 00:10:25.120
How bustling.

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:26.240
Why don't we try our luck?

00:10:27.320 --> 00:10:28.270
Sure.

00:10:39.600 --> 00:10:40.440
Yunzhou,

00:10:41.550 --> 00:10:42.390
I...

00:10:42.750 --> 00:10:43.910
We've been walking all day.

00:10:44.360 --> 00:10:45.870
My legs are feeling a bit sore.

00:10:46.390 --> 00:10:48.200
Shall we come back another time?

00:10:48.933 --> 00:10:50.000
I should've noticed sooner.

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:51.600
Let me walk you back.

00:10:51.600 --> 00:10:53.080
Help!

00:10:54.030 --> 00:10:54.870
Mother!

00:10:56.000 --> 00:10:57.120
Yuan, be careful!

00:11:01.720 --> 00:11:03.120
Father, Mother, this way!

00:11:03.360 --> 00:11:04.200
Go!

00:11:08.700 --> 00:11:11.500
(Tongchen Inn)

00:11:16.870 --> 00:11:17.960
Father, Mother,

00:11:18.360 --> 00:11:19.200
the day has broken.

00:11:19.510 --> 00:11:21.000
We found shelter here for the night.

00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:22.080
Now, it seems we're safe.

00:11:22.630 --> 00:11:23.750
Let's set off and return.

00:11:25.200 --> 00:11:26.150
Sure.

00:11:38.080 --> 00:11:38.960
How dare you!

00:11:39.390 --> 00:11:41.080
Killing an official is rebellion,

00:11:41.340 --> 00:11:42.493
punishable by clan execution.

00:11:42.790 --> 00:11:44.030
Do you truly dare?

00:12:18.200 --> 00:12:20.680
So, you are Chancellor Jiang's daughter.

00:12:42.940 --> 00:12:44.460
♪The dream shattered♪

00:12:44.820 --> 00:12:46.500
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

00:12:46.500 --> 00:12:48.140
♪Like a restless soul♪

00:12:49.020 --> 00:12:50.580
♪How vague♪

00:12:50.980 --> 00:12:52.500
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

00:12:52.500 --> 00:12:54.740
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

00:12:55.540 --> 00:12:58.140
♪Love and hate entwined♪

00:12:58.620 --> 00:13:01.460
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

00:13:02.100 --> 00:13:06.860
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

00:13:07.460 --> 00:13:08.980
♪When fate falls apart♪

00:13:09.380 --> 00:13:12.940
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

00:13:13.660 --> 00:13:15.220
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

00:13:15.620 --> 00:13:19.340
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

00:13:20.060 --> 00:13:22.900
♪Life after life♪

00:13:23.380 --> 00:13:26.060
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

00:13:26.700 --> 00:13:30.780
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

00:13:30.860 --> 00:13:33.900
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

00:13:34.060 --> 00:13:35.460
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

00:13:35.460 --> 00:13:38.580
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

00:13:38.660 --> 00:13:40.100
♪Now shatter apart♪

00:13:40.220 --> 00:13:43.980
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

00:13:44.700 --> 00:13:47.500
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

00:13:47.780 --> 00:13:50.620
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

00:13:50.940 --> 00:13:55.340
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

00:13:55.580 --> 00:13:58.500
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

00:13:58.620 --> 00:14:03.060
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

00:14:03.260 --> 00:14:08.980
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

00:14:09.420 --> 00:14:12.140
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

00:14:12.380 --> 00:14:15.100
♪Sober or indulge♪

00:14:15.540 --> 00:14:21.540
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪